creator: Greener Technologies LLC
descriptionHtml:
Greener makes daily lawn-care perfection possible by automating your landscaper’s routine tasks—mowing, monitoring and maintenance—freeing them up to focus their weekly visits on premium groundskeeping work while your lawn stays at its ideal length every single day.

With the Greener app, homeowners get access to an on-demand dashboard that connects them to our full complement of services, including scheduling and naming of their automated mowers, handy access to monthly progress reports, and one-tap reporting of any lawn-care issues or concerns.
